node.text:
Glad to reveal my first cover with you all!! 🎼🎶🎵🎸
Thank you @alf_nsong for introducing me to this song.

At first I thought recording a live take wouldn't be too hard, but by the time we tried to do a 4th take, we couldn't even finish the song. Don't even mention the 5th and 6th take 😂

Thank you @sognohk for lending such an amazing venue for us to perform in! 🙏

It's also a real pleasure to have @aaryncheung guide me through my first cover, learning that guitar solo was definitely not an easy feat. 

Learned a lot from this experience but also a lot of room for improvement for me, I hope you all enjoy this song as much as we enjoyed singing it! Hopefully there will be a lot more covers  to come!!

This cover is also on YouTube! Click the link in my bio! Remember to like and subscribe 😁

Director - @lam_ting_hin
Stylist - @imkarenatang
Song - Cyclone by Sticky Fingers

#cyclone #stickyfingers #sognohk
